---------------------

found   : function (new:Date, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?): string
expected: function (new:Date, ?=, ?=, ?=, ?=, ?=, ?=, ?=): string
function Date(opt_yr_num, opt_mo_num, opt_day_num, opt_hr_num, opt_min_num,
^
----------------------

/ Fredrik
The fix has been submitted in the internal repository it should be pushed out tomorrow.
